      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can't shut my brain off at all. im already taking like 5mg of melatonin every night but it isnt really doing much anymore. my doctor just gave me a prescription for zolpidem (ambien) to help me out, but i was wondering if its okay to take the melatonin and the ambien together? i feel like if i take both it might actually work better so i can finally get some rest.",
